Just upgraded from 1.2.2 now that mods are updated.  Here is a crash log.

https://www.dropbox.com/s/xhjj6zjd78ky10u/output_log.txt?dl=0

Might be Orbital Survey Plus, but I deleted and still shows up.
A quick glance at your log shows that you have MM 2.7.2 installed, which isn't compatible with KSP 1.3.1. I would go through your mods and make sure all of them are compatible with 1.3.1.
I put them all in through CKAN...  Will check.  Thank you.
Open the output.log and search for "CompatibleKspVersionMax: False". There are at least eleven old mods.
